headline: Match Group to Present at the Citi Global TMT Conference
summary: Match Group (NASDAQ: MTCH) announced today that Steven Bailey, Chief Financial Officer of Match Group, will participate in a fireside chat at the Citi Global TMT Conference on Wednesday, September 3rd at 10:50 a.m. Eastern Time (ET). A live webcast and replay of the fireside chat will be available at https://ir.mtch.com/investor-relations/news-events/events-archive/default.aspx.
